title: Episode 03
description:
On today’s tapes…

>> Babysitter
A man recounts his dreams about a former babysitter… or maybe they’re nightmares.

>> Game Store Creep
A woman has an odd interaction with a customer… then she receives a phone call.

>> What Was She Planning?
A man is brought home from the bar by a stranger… but the house isn’t empty.
